Disclaimer:
This plugin only works agains pre 0.5 versions of Backbone.  

Useage:

In your controller you can now add:

before: {
	'some_route_regex' : before_func,
	'some_other_route_regex' : before_func2,	
},

after: {
	'some_route_regex' : after_func,
	'some_other_route_regex' : after_func2,	
}

Your filters will be called and if a filter returns false, the filter chain is halted.
If a before filter chain is halted, the action in the controller will not be called.